He's our best shot at finding Manta,

510
00:52:47,160 --> 00:52:49,540
你若跑去它面前大秀肌肉
and he's not going to tell us anything if you go in there

511
00:52:49,540 --> 00:52:51,330
它是什么都不会说的
flexing your muscles at him.

512
00:52:53,750 --> 00:52:56,380
你很幸运我俩没有一起长大 小弟
You're so lucky we didn't grow up together, little brother.

513
00:52:57,800 --> 00:52:59,920
别叫我小弟
Do not call me "brother."

514
00:53:00,550 --> 00:53:01,880
唉唷唷
Well...

515
00:53:02,260 --> 00:53:06,220
真是个大惊喜
This is a bit of a surprise, isn't it?

516
00:53:06,640 --> 00:53:09,640
我没想到你已经被监狱释放了
I didn't realize you'd been released from prison.

517
00:53:09,640 --> 00:53:12,560
我是最近才出狱的
It is a recent development.

518
00:53:12,940 --> 00:53:16,690
反正我们都是亡命之徒 对吧?
Outlaws, aren't we all?

519
00:53:17,520 --> 00:53:19,570
我们需要找到大卫凯恩
We need to find David Kane.

520
00:53:20,240 --> 00:53:22,860
关于那点 恐怕我有坏消息
Bad news, I'm afraid.

521
00:53:22,860 --> 00:53:26,490
大卫凯恩现在不接生意了
David Kane is no longer on the market.

522
00:53:26,490 --> 00:53:29,040
多少钱都不接
Not for sale at any price.

523
00:53:29,580 --> 00:53:34,120
他现在自己当老板 单打独斗
He's solely running as an independent operator.

524
00:53:34,540 --> 00:53:36,210
他的藏身处在哪?
Where is he holed up now?

525
00:53:39,760 --> 00:53:42,170
作为交换 我可以让
In exchange, I offer a favor...

526
00:53:43,260 --> 00:53:46,800
亚特兰提斯之王欠你一次情
from the King of Atlantis.

527
00:53:48,600 --> 00:53:50,810
你难不成真想让我跟那种
You seriously expect me to play footsie with someone

528
00:53:50,810 --> 00:53:52,730
满手血腥的家伙打交道?
with that kind of blood on their hands?

529
00:53:52,730 --> 00:53:55,230
可我没有手
I don't have hands!

530
00:53:55,230 --> 00:53:57,020
也没有脚
Or feet!

531
00:54:02,860 --> 00:54:06,530
听着 若是你提供的情报核实无误
Listen, if the information checks out good,

532
00:54:06,530 --> 00:54:11,200
我保证我不会立刻回来拆了这地方
I promise you that I won't immediately come back here and tear this place apart.

533
00:54:13,120 --> 00:54:15,120
那真是太可惜了
That's too bad.

534
00:54:16,040 --> 00:54:22,090
道上规矩是亚特兰提斯之王 向来对沉没堡垒睁一只眼闭一只眼
Traditionally, the kings of Atlantis have turned a blind eye to the Sunken Citadel.

535
00:54:22,840 --> 00:54:26,890
现在看来我们得手动替你闭眼了
Now, we have to blind it for you.

536
00:54:35,020 --> 00:54:37,230
算了 你来大秀肌肉吧
Fine. Flex your muscles.

537
00:54:49,370 --> 00:54:51,160
快打爆他的鸟头
Smash his stupid head in!

538
00:54:52,410 --> 00:54:53,450
吃我一拳
Boom!

539
00:55:09,220 --> 00:55:10,470
抓到你了 死胖子
Gotcha, fatback!

540
00:55:13,850 --> 00:55:16,940
好啦好啦 万事好商量 我们聊聊
Okay! Okay! We can work this out. We can.

541
00:55:16,940 --> 00:55:18,150
那你说啊
Talk.

542
00:55:18,150 --> 00:55:21,190
我不知道他在哪 但最近有不少谣传
I don't know where he is, but there have been rumors.

543
00:55:21,190 --> 00:55:25,400
南太平洋一个叫魔鬼深渊的休眠火山
A dormant volcano in the South Pacific, called "Devil's Deep."

544
00:55:26,110 --> 00:55:27,360
再说快点
Talk faster.

545
00:55:27,360 --> 00:55:28,950
那里曾经荒芜多年
It's been barren for years.

546
00:55:28,950 --> 00:55:31,160
但旅人说最近当地出现丛林
But travelers say there's a jungle there now.

547
00:55:31,160 --> 00:55:33,910
船只一旦靠近当地导航系统就会错乱
Navigation gets scrambled as soon as you start to get close.

548
00:55:33,910 --> 00:55:36,910
若是太靠近 就会有去无回
And if you get too close, you don't come back!

549
00:55:36,910 --> 00:55:39,960
若要我猜 而我真的是乱猜的
If I was a betting man, and believe me, I am,

550
00:55:39,960 --> 00:55:42,590
我会说大卫凯恩藏在那里
I'd say that's where Kane is hiding out.

551
00:55:45,920 --> 00:55:47,420
消息打听到了 我们走
We got all we needed. Let's go!

552
00:55:59,140 --> 00:56:02,820
崛起 来吧 从火中崛起
♪ Rise up, come Rise up through the fire ♪

553
00:56:08,610 --> 00:56:10,910
很快你就会比他更为强大
Soon you'll be more powerful than he is.

554
00:56:11,530 --> 00:56:16,450
但你还没准备好 而且你太快让他入局了
But you're not ready yet, and you involved him far too soon.

555
00:56:16,450 --> 00:56:19,250
我能感觉到他们的追兵
I sense them closing in on us.

556
00:56:19,250 --> 00:56:20,670
我看起来很担心吗?
Do I seem concerned?

557
00:56:22,840 --> 00:56:25,250
其实这样反而更方便
If anything, it's even easier now.

558
00:56:25,880 --> 00:56:28,090
比我们原本自己计划得更...
We couldn't have planned it any better than...

559
00:56:36,470 --> 00:56:41,310
嗨 我只是想告诉你奥利哈钢熔炉
Hey. I... I just wanted to tell you that the orichalcum furnace

560
00:56:41,310 --> 00:56:43,230
现在正在以最大值输出
is now running at peak output.

561
00:56:55,830 --> 00:57:00,960
（南太平洋某处）

562
00:57:09,470 --> 00:57:15,680
（魔鬼深渊）

563
00:57:35,910 --> 00:57:36,910
我赢了
I win.

564
00:57:41,410 --> 00:57:44,710
土拨 回亚特兰提斯通报我们的方位
Topo, go back to Atlantis and give them our coordinates.

565
00:57:52,840 --> 00:57:54,390
你知道现在有什么会很棒吗?
You know what'd be amazing right now?

566
00:57:54,390 --> 00:57:55,390
援兵?
Reinforcements?

567
00:57:55,390 --> 00:57:58,350
超大又多汁的起司汉堡 再加上一大杯黑啤酒
Great, big, greasy cheeseburger and a pint of Guinness.

568
00:57:59,810 --> 00:58:02,180
你得承认 陆地的食物真的好吃很多
You gotta admit, the food is so much better up here.

569
00:58:02,180 --> 00:58:03,640
这种说法有点离谱
I find that hard to believe.

570
00:58:03,640 --> 00:58:05,100
等等
Hold up.

571
00:58:05,100 --> 00:58:07,190
你是说你从没为了起司汉堡上岸过?
You telling me you never went topside to have a cheeseburger?

572
00:58:07,190 --> 00:58:09,780
-什么? -或是为了腊肠披萨?
- What? - Or a slice of 'za? Pepperoni?

573
00:58:10,690 --> 00:58:14,610
或是为了超厚半生牛排 配上薯条和奶昔 再沾上...
Or a thick, juicy, medium raw steak with fries and a shake, and you dip it...

574
00:58:14,610 --> 00:58:18,950
就连陆地居民食物的名称 听起来都很恶心
Even the words that surface-dwellers give their food sound disgusting.

575
00:58:20,950 --> 00:58:23,580
因为偏见 你失去享受半个世界的乐趣
You've let your prejudices stop you from enjoying half the world.

576
00:58:24,160 --> 00:58:27,380
你该好好反思 那是你的损失 兄弟
You should think about that. It's your loss, dude.

577
00:58:36,010 --> 00:58:37,430
好耶
Aw, yeah!

578
00:58:37,430 --> 00:58:38,850
我打赌你从没吃过这个
Bet you never had one of these.

579
00:58:39,720 --> 00:58:41,560
-那是什么? -蟑螂
- What is it? - It's a cockroach.

580
00:58:42,730 --> 00:58:43,520
你们会吃这个?
You eat it?

581
00:58:43,520 --> 00:58:45,440
对啊 这等同陆地的鲜虾
Oh, yeah. Shrimp of the land.

582
00:59:02,450 --> 00:59:04,960
对吧 很好吃 来 这个给你喝
Eh? That's good. Here, drink this.

583
00:59:09,210 --> 00:59:10,380
好 你先请
Okay, you first.

584
00:59:43,870 --> 00:59:45,250
你有看到这个吗?
Are you seeing this?

585
00:59:48,330 --> 00:59:49,420
这不正常吗?
That's not normal?

586
00:59:54,340 --> 00:59:55,760
肯定不正常
Definitely not normal. Ugh.

587
00:59:59,550 --> 01:00:02,930
我们走吧 现在你知道奥利哈钢有多危险了
Let's get out of here. You see how dangerous the orichalcum can be?

588
01:00:02,930 --> 01:00:06,060
我打赌那在短时间内 让岛上动植物都变异了
I bet it mutated the flora and fauna in a short amount of time,

589
01:00:06,060 --> 01:00:08,770
变得超...巨大
turning them... monstrous.

590
01:00:19,150 --> 01:00:20,070
糟糕
Oh, shit...

591
01:00:31,960 --> 01:00:32,790
快逃啊
Run!

592
01:00:36,090 --> 01:00:37,010
快点
Come on.

593
01:00:39,630 --> 01:00:40,680
再跑快点
Faster!

594
01:00:47,560 --> 01:00:48,770
你在耍什么宝?
What the hell are you doing?

595
01:00:49,350 --> 01:00:50,850
我不知道 我不太习惯跑步
I don't know. I'm not used to running.

596
01:00:50,850 --> 01:00:51,980
跟着我做
Just do what I do.

597
01:00:51,980 --> 01:00:53,770
用手臂和腿 手刀摆动起来
Use your arms, use your legs. Lift them up.

598
01:00:54,440 --> 01:00:55,440
像这样吗?
Like this?

599
01:00:57,400 --> 01:00:58,860
-你不是吧 -好耶
- Holy shit. - Yeah!

600
01:00:58,860 --> 01:01:00,280
-等等我 -好耶
- Wait up. - Yeah!

601
01:01:32,730 --> 01:01:34,440
我们得跳下去 这高度摔不死
We have to jump. We'll survive the fall.

602
01:01:34,440 --> 01:01:36,150
你疯了吗? 那会很痛
Are you crazy? It's gonna hurt.

603
01:01:36,150 --> 01:01:38,940
不然你想怎样? 留在这里跟跳跳鬼打一架?
What do you wanna do, stay here and fight the hopping demons?

604
01:01:40,190 --> 01:01:42,110
那是什么? 上面写什么?
What is that? What does that say?

605
01:01:42,110 --> 01:01:43,700
那是古老的亚特兰提斯语
The writing is ancient Atlantean.

606
01:01:43,700 --> 01:01:46,780
"真正的王者搭建桥梁"
"A true king builds bridges."

607
01:01:51,460 --> 01:01:52,500
你想干嘛?
What are you doing?

608
01:01:57,800 --> 01:01:59,510
你还有比这更瞎的主意吗?
Got any more krill-brained ideas?

609
01:02:27,950 --> 01:02:30,370
你看 真正的王者搭建桥梁
See? A true king builds bridges.

610
01:02:33,080 --> 01:02:34,210
那只是一种隐喻
That's a metaphor!

611
01:02:35,000 --> 01:02:37,080
喔对 我忘记告诉你了
Hey! I forgot to tell you.

612
01:02:37,080 --> 01:02:38,500
老妈说她很爱你
Mom says she loves you.

613
01:02:38,500 --> 01:02:40,590
也总是想着你
She thinks about you all the time.

614
01:02:40,590 --> 01:02:42,670
你干嘛挑现在告诉我?
Why the hell are you telling me this now?

615
01:02:42,670 --> 01:02:45,340
我也不知道 懒得等待适当时机了
I don't know. I'm just tired of waiting for the right moment.

616
01:02:52,220 --> 01:02:53,230
快点
Come on.

617
01:03:21,380 --> 01:03:23,840
看来我的隐喻刚救了你一命
Looks like my metaphor just saved your ass.

618
01:03:33,640 --> 01:03:36,770
大卫 我刚才做了更多测试 但这些数据很让人忧心
Uh, David? I just ran more tests, and this data is really disturbing.

619
01:03:36,770 --> 01:03:39,690
我们得停止燃烧奥利哈钢
We have to stop burning the... orichalcum.

620
01:03:42,230 --> 01:03:43,230
大卫?
David?

621
01:04:52,300 --> 01:04:57,600
好吧 博士 既然你这么想知道我的大计
Okay, doc, you want to know my plan so bad.

622
01:04:58,680 --> 01:05:00,020
那就告诉你吧
Here it is.

623
01:05:00,890 --> 01:05:04,690
我要干掉海王 毁掉他所珍视的一切
I'm gonna kill Aquaman and destroy everything he holds dear.

624
01:05:05,820 --> 01:05:11,160
我要杀光他的家人 将他的王国焚烧殆尽
I'm gonna murder his family and burn his kingdom to ash.

625
01:05:12,160 --> 01:05:15,950
我会为我父亲报仇
I will avenge my father.

626
01:05:16,620 --> 01:05:19,910
就算得跟魔鬼交易也没问题
Even if I have to make a deal with the devil to do it.

627
01:05:21,170 --> 01:05:24,080
大卫 你不能信任那支三叉戟
David, you can't trust the trident.

628
01:05:29,090 --> 01:05:34,550
我从不轻易拔出这把匕首 除非确定能见血
I never draw this blade unless it's gonna taste blood.

629
01:05:37,010 --> 01:05:39,600
你最好祈祷我不会再对你拔刀
Pray I never show it to you again.

630
01:06:03,960 --> 01:06:06,210
我们肯定接近放射源了
We must be getting close to the radiation source.

631
01:06:06,670 --> 01:06:08,960
我们该先等亚特兰提斯 接到通报再行动
We should wait for Atlantis to receive your message.

632
01:06:08,960 --> 01:06:10,760
目前可以先行侦察
We can conduct reconnaissance in the meantime.

633
01:06:10,760 --> 01:06:13,760
好喔 洛基 没人在问你的意见
Yeah. Look, Loki, I'm not asking for your advice on this.

634
01:06:13,760 --> 01:06:15,680
你已经完成你的阶段任务
You've already lived up to your end of the deal.

635
01:06:15,680 --> 01:06:18,100
欢迎你随时返回阿兹卡班
So you can go on back to Azkaban for all I care.

636
01:06:18,100 --> 01:06:19,640
那你有何计划?
So, what's your plan?

637
01:06:19,640 --> 01:06:20,970
我没计划
I don't have one, yet.

638
01:06:20,970 --> 01:06:24,060
但他攻击我妻子 所以我非搞死他不可
But he came after my wife, which means I'm gonna pull his tongue out of his butt.

639
01:06:24,600 --> 01:06:27,270
亚瑟 你是国王 不可意气用事
Arthur, you are the king. You cannot let this get personal.

640
01:06:27,690 --> 01:06:29,940
当初拿整个王国来赌气的人
This coming from the guy who turned the entire nation of Atlantis

641
01:06:29,940 --> 01:06:31,610
也好意思这么说?
into his own private ego trip?

642
01:06:31,610 --> 01:06:32,740
我赌气?
My ego?

643
01:06:32,740 --> 01:06:35,990
是你自己先来踢馆挑战我的王位
You're the one who swam through the front gate and challenged my claim for the throne.

644
01:06:35,990 --> 01:06:38,280
那只是因为你想毁灭陆地世界
Only because you're trying to destroy the surface world.

645
01:06:38,280 --> 01:06:40,660
若你没有那么恶劣 现在还会是国王
If you weren't such an asshole, you'd still be king.

646
01:06:41,540 --> 01:06:42,330
太扯了
Unbelievable.

647
01:06:42,870 --> 01:06:43,750
等等 等等
Wait, wait! Wait!

648
01:06:43,750 --> 01:06:46,330
你抢了我的王位却根本不想要?
You took my throne and you don't even want it?

649
01:06:46,330 --> 01:06:49,040
你是在搞笑吧? 我恨死这工作了
Are you kidding me? I hate this job.

650
01:06:49,040 --> 01:06:52,010
我这样做纯粹是为了 防止亚特兰提斯毁灭陆地世界
Only reason I'm doing it is to keep Atlantis from destroying the surface.

651
01:06:52,010 --> 01:06:53,720
而且我很可能正越搞越糟
And I might even be screwing that up.

652
01:06:53,720 --> 01:06:55,010
你真的无心王位?
You really had no ambition for it?

653
01:06:55,010 --> 01:06:56,180
完全无意
Absolutely not.

654
01:06:56,720 --> 01:06:58,850
从我父亲发现你存在的那天起
From the day my father found out you existed,

655
01:06:58,850 --> 01:07:00,600
他就训练我做好准备
he prepared me for the moment that you would come

656
01:07:00,600 --> 01:07:01,850
以防你有朝一日来篡位
and challenge me for the throne.

657
01:07:01,850 --> 01:07:03,480
那也太可悲了
Wow, that's really sad.

658
01:07:03,480 --> 01:07:04,980
特别是我那么容易就打趴你
Especially when you think how easily I kicked your ass

659
01:07:04,980 --> 01:07:06,810
根本不需准备工作
with basically no prep time whatsoever.

660
01:07:08,150 --> 01:07:09,150
打脸了
Roasted.

661
01:07:09,690 --> 01:07:11,320
事情经过不是那样的
That is not how it happened.

662
01:07:11,320 --> 01:07:12,940
-事情的经过正是如此 -是梅拉救了你
- That's exactly how it happened. - Mera saved you.

663
01:07:12,940 --> 01:07:14,400
她才没有 是我自己打趴你
No, she didn't. I kicked your ass.

664
01:07:14,400 --> 01:07:17,030
才怪 她操纵了水龙卷 我被卷入其中
Nope. She made the little water tornado. I fell in it.

665
01:07:17,030 --> 01:07:18,490
闭嘴 我们应该到了
Okay, shut up. I think we're here.

666
01:07:28,880 --> 01:07:30,170
来吧 我们上吧
Come on, let's do this.

667
01:07:30,170 --> 01:07:32,760
等一切完事后 我们该去吃汉堡喝啤酒
Once this is over with, we should go get some burgers and beers.

668
01:07:32,760 --> 01:07:34,840
-别得寸进尺 -塔可和龙舌兰酒
- Don't push it. - Tacos and tequila.

669
01:07:34,840 --> 01:07:36,380
根本没听过那些东西
I don't even know those words.

670
01:08:03,660 --> 01:08:04,700
喂
Hey!

671
01:08:38,860 --> 01:08:40,110
等等 小弟
Whoa, brother.

672
01:08:50,790 --> 01:08:52,380
那是奥利哈钢熔炉
It's an orichalcum furnace.

673
01:08:53,670 --> 01:08:55,170
所有被偷走的奥利哈钢
All that stolen orichalcum.

674
01:08:55,170 --> 01:08:56,920
就这样烧个不停
They're just burning it up.

675
01:08:56,920 --> 01:08:58,920
他是故意要让大气升温
He's heating the atmosphere on purpose.

676
01:08:59,300 --> 01:09:00,840
这真是大灾难
This is catastrophic.

677
01:09:01,260 --> 01:09:02,930
这地方肯定有隔热罩
This whole place must be heat-shielded

678
01:09:02,930 --> 01:09:05,310
好躲过地表热能卫星的侦测
to protect it from the surface's thermal satellites.

679
01:09:05,890 --> 01:09:07,350
问题是 要怎么阻止?
Question is, how do we stop 'em?

680
01:09:07,350 --> 01:09:10,520
要摧毁这些反应炉 我们必须夷平整座岛屿
To take out this reactor, we would have to crater the entire island.

681
01:09:10,520 --> 01:09:12,600
离控制台远点
Get away from there! Now!

682
01:09:14,480 --> 01:09:18,780
这把雷射枪可能很古老 却是专为杀死亚特兰提斯人而制成
This blaster may be ancient, but it was built for killing Atlanteans.

683
01:09:25,080 --> 01:09:27,240
好 很抱歉 我不是那个意思
Okay, I am so sorry. I did not mean that.

684
01:09:27,240 --> 01:09:29,830
我只是怕你们会在我投降前先打死我
I just didn't want you to break me in half before I could surrender.

685
01:09:31,500 --> 01:09:32,710
求你们带我走
Please take me with you.

686
01:09:34,380 --> 01:09:36,340
敲昏他 然后帮我把这些人藏起来
Knock him out and then help me hide these bodies.

687
01:09:36,960 --> 01:09:38,340
不 等等 拜托
No, no. Wait, please.

688
01:09:39,130 --> 01:09:40,670
这完全不是我的本意
I didn't want any of this.

689
01:09:40,670 --> 01:09:43,890
我原本只是想亲眼目睹亚特兰提斯
All I wanted was to see Atlantis with my own eyes.

690
01:09:43,890 --> 01:09:46,100
我以为可以跟世界分享这奇迹
I thought I could share its wonders with the world.

691
01:09:46,100 --> 01:09:49,560
我是科学家 只想被认真对待
I'm a scientist, and I just wanted to be taken seriously.

692
01:09:50,350 --> 01:09:53,310
大卫凯恩说他能帮我 但现在他不放我离开
David Kane said he could help me, but now he won't let me leave.

693
01:09:53,310 --> 01:09:56,520
你指望我们相信你跟这一切无关?
You expect us to believe you have nothing to do with this?

694
01:09:57,570 --> 01:09:58,690
我知道
I know.

695
01:09:59,190 --> 01:10:00,780
我做了些很不光彩的事
I've done things I'm not proud of.

696
01:10:01,360 --> 01:10:03,110
但若我不照办他就会杀了我
But he would've killed me if I hadn't.

697
01:10:05,120 --> 01:10:06,120
敲昏他
Knock him out.

698
01:10:07,280 --> 01:10:08,160
不要
No.

699
01:10:08,700 --> 01:10:10,410
-那我来敲昏他 -不行
- Then I'll knock him out. - No!

700
01:10:11,620 --> 01:10:12,790
-什么? -不行
- What? - No.

701
01:10:14,670 --> 01:10:15,790
好啦
Fine!

702
01:10:16,790 --> 01:10:18,050
你可以跟我们一起走
You can come with us.

703
01:10:19,050 --> 01:10:19,880
谢谢你们
Oh... thank you.

704
01:10:19,880 --> 01:10:22,880
但你最好从实招来 否则就会被我毒打
But you better start talking. Or I'm gonna give you one sasa!

705
01:10:22,880 --> 01:10:24,260
好啦 好啦
Okay, okay.

706
01:10:24,260 --> 01:10:27,970
是那支黑色三叉戟 它连结着某种上古邪灵
It's the black trident. It's a direct link to some ancient evil.

707
01:10:27,970 --> 01:10:29,680
它赋予凯恩强大力量 作为回馈...
It gives Kane great powers and in return...

708
01:10:47,320 --> 01:10:49,540
我讨厌被炸飞
I hate when that happens.

709
01:11:02,420 --> 01:11:03,760
阻止他们
Stop them!

710
01:13:17,100 --> 01:13:19,730
不不 别用奥利哈钢
No, no, no, no, no! Not the orichalcum!

711
01:13:19,730 --> 01:13:20,980
你想炸飞我们吗?
You wanna blow us up?

712
01:13:20,980 --> 01:13:22,770
-这东西会爆炸? -对
- This stuff blows up? - Yes!

713
01:13:22,770 --> 01:13:23,810
不好意思
My bad!

714
01:13:27,440 --> 01:13:29,240
那就别用它来打斗
Then stop using it!

715
01:13:29,740 --> 01:13:31,490
闭嘴乖乖等我来救你
Just shut up and let me save your ass.

716
01:13:32,200 --> 01:13:33,200
又一次
Again.

717
01:14:56,490 --> 01:14:58,910
他要不穿动力装甲跟我们打?
He's going to fight us without the power suit?

718
01:14:58,910 --> 01:15:00,740
我跟你说过他变强大了
I told you he's stronger now.

719
01:15:01,950 --> 01:15:03,710
但他还是一个陆地居民
He's still just a surface-dweller.

720
01:15:12,670 --> 01:15:13,380
小弟
Bro!

721
01:15:18,970 --> 01:15:23,020
我从未想过会看到你俩并肩作战
I never expected to see you two fighting side by side.

722
01:15:23,020 --> 01:15:25,390
我们是特地为你合体的
We're making a special exception just for you.

723
01:15:30,730 --> 01:15:33,280
谁都不准揍我弟 除了我以外
No one hits my brother but me.

724
01:15:33,280 --> 01:15:37,780
我原本打算最后再去杀你 但多谢你主动来访
I was gonna kill you last, but thanks for dropping by.

725
01:15:37,780 --> 01:15:39,490
你让我省了好多麻烦
You're making this easy.

726
01:15:53,090 --> 01:15:53,880
对
Yeah!

727
01:15:54,470 --> 01:15:55,340
放马过来
Come at me,

728
01:15:55,340 --> 01:15:56,680
杀手级国王组
the killer of kings.

729
01:16:57,280 --> 01:16:58,860
夷平这座岛
Take that island down!

730
01:17:22,050 --> 01:17:23,390
自由开火
Fire at will!

731
01:17:35,230 --> 01:17:36,820
我们得尽快离开这里
We've got to get out of here.

732
01:17:47,290 --> 01:17:50,330
故障 故障 警告 警告
Malfunction. Malfunction. Warning. Warning.

733
01:18:16,400 --> 01:18:17,940
老沈 快点
Shin, let's go!

734
01:18:23,200 --> 01:18:24,570
你还在等什么?
What are you waiting for?

735
01:18:24,570 --> 01:18:26,530
快发射音波炮
Fire the goddamn cannon!

736
01:19:30,350 --> 01:19:31,850
抱歉害你们卷入这一切
I'm sorry to drag you all into this.

737
01:19:31,850 --> 01:19:34,440
但我们不能让人鱼王国知道 亚特兰提斯有介入
But the Fishermen can't think that Atlantis was involved.

738
01:19:34,440 --> 01:19:37,770
泽贝尔的军队归我管 不归亚特兰提斯管
Atlantis does not command the armies of Xebel. I do.

739
01:19:37,770 --> 01:19:41,280
我们盐海王国仍然记得你的恩情
And the Brine Kingdom has not forgotten its debt to you.

740
01:19:41,280 --> 01:19:42,940
有事总是可以找我们相助
You may count on us always.

741
01:19:43,740 --> 01:19:45,110
当我手握黑色三叉戟时
Something happened to me.

742
01:19:45,900 --> 01:19:48,030
有奇怪的事发生在我身上
When I touched that black trident.

743
01:19:48,570 --> 01:19:50,160
他为何在这里?
Why is he even here?

744
01:19:50,870 --> 01:19:52,540
他该在返回监狱的路上
He should be on his way back to prison.

745
01:19:52,540 --> 01:19:54,250
我们该听听他要说什么
We should hear what he has to say.

746
01:19:54,250 --> 01:19:56,120
这种错我犯过一次
I made that mistake once.

747
01:19:56,120 --> 01:19:58,290
所以我知道不该相信他
That's why I know he can't be trusted.

748
01:19:58,290 --> 01:20:01,090
他还砍断我的螯足
And he cut off my claw.

749
01:20:01,840 --> 01:20:04,340
花了一整年才长回来
This thing took a whole year to grow back.

750
01:20:04,340 --> 01:20:06,800
听着 他跟我们一样想阻止黑蝠鲼
Look, he wants to stop Manta same as we do.

751
01:20:06,800 --> 01:20:08,640
说句公道话
And just for the record,

752
01:20:08,640 --> 01:20:10,850
多亏了他我们才能追查到这里
the only reason we made it this far is because of him.

753
01:20:13,100 --> 01:20:14,520
我看到了失落王国
I saw the Lost Kingdom.

754
01:20:18,350 --> 01:20:21,020
妈 我对这些事了解不够深
Mom, I don't know enough about this.

755
01:20:21,020 --> 01:20:22,610
这有可能吗?
Is that even possible?

756
01:20:23,070 --> 01:20:26,070
大家只确切知道 曾有第七个王国的存在
All anyone knows for sure is there once was a seventh kingdom

757
01:20:26,070 --> 01:20:29,160
然后在大沉没前的某天
and then one day, just before the fall,

758
01:20:29,160 --> 01:20:31,740
该国历史被从所有史书中抹去
every record of it was stricken from the chronicles.

759
01:20:32,370 --> 01:20:34,950
你怎么知道你看到的就是失落王国?
How do you know what you saw was the Lost Kingdom?

760
01:20:34,950 --> 01:20:37,960
大家甚至不知道它的国名
No one even knows what it was called anymore.

761
01:20:37,960 --> 01:20:39,580
它叫涅库斯
It's called Necrus.

762
01:20:40,630 --> 01:20:42,210
我不仅仅有看到
And I didn't just see it.

763
01:20:43,550 --> 01:20:44,590
我还心知肚明
I knew it.

764
01:20:46,510 --> 01:20:49,510
那感觉就像是回忆起往日
It's almost like I was... remembering it.

765
01:20:51,010 --> 01:20:54,390
陌生的记忆突然涌入脑海
Flashes of someone else's memories.

766
01:20:55,270 --> 01:21:00,020
在亚特兰王在位期间 亚特兰提斯由七个联合王国组成
During King Atlan's time, there were seven united kingdoms of Atlantis.

767
01:21:01,440 --> 01:21:05,320
而黑城就像是万恶的根源
And the Black City was a curse upon them all.

768
01:21:12,160 --> 01:21:13,990
借由滥采奥利哈钢
By exploiting orichalcum,

769
01:21:13,990 --> 01:21:17,250
涅库斯很快就成为超级强权
Necrus rapidly became a superpower unlike any other.

770
01:21:17,250 --> 01:21:19,160
但这带来惨痛的代价
But it came at a terrible price.

771
01:21:19,580 --> 01:21:21,580
污染陆地与海洋
Poisoning the land, the sea,

772
01:21:22,420 --> 01:21:25,340
就连掌管涅库斯的暴君心智都被戕害
even the mind of the tyrant who ruled Necrus.

773
01:21:28,630 --> 01:21:31,180
也就是亚特兰的亲弟弟寇达斯
Atlan's own brother, Kordax.

774
01:21:31,930 --> 01:21:37,020
亚特兰央求他在造成 世界不可逆的损害前停止
Atlan pleaded with him to stop using it before the world was irrevocably damaged.

775
01:21:37,020 --> 01:21:39,600
然而寇达斯却憎恨亚特兰
However, Kordax resented Atlan,

776
01:21:39,600 --> 01:21:42,600
认为自己大哥只想窃取他的力量
thinking his own brother was trying to steal his power.

777
01:21:42,980 --> 01:21:47,230
所以他求助黑魔法 并打造出邪恶法器
So, he resorted to dark magic and crafted an instrument of evil.

778
01:21:48,030 --> 01:21:49,450
就是那黑色三叉戟
That black trident.

779
01:21:58,700 --> 01:22:02,420
他将自己和子民幻化成怪兽
He transformed his people and himself into monsters...

780
01:22:06,500 --> 01:22:07,920
好对抗亚特兰提斯
...to fight Atlantis.

781
01:22:08,630 --> 01:22:10,300
两兄弟因此兵戎相见
So, the two brothers went to war.

782
01:22:19,600 --> 01:22:24,520
但亚特兰击败了寇达斯 并用自己的鲜血施下魔咒
But Atlan defeated Kordax and imprisoned him and all of Necrus

783
01:22:24,520 --> 01:22:27,480
好将他与涅库斯人民全数囚禁
with a spell cast with his own blood...

784
01:22:30,820 --> 01:22:34,320
以确保寇达斯的黑魔法永远消失
...to ensure that Kordax's dark power would never be found.

785
01:22:36,030 --> 01:22:38,700
涅库斯也因此被从史书中抹去
And that is why Necrus is stricken from the chronicles.

786
01:22:50,050 --> 01:22:53,300
邪恶力量原本该永世被冰封
This evil was supposed to remain frozen for eternity.

787
01:22:55,680 --> 01:22:57,680
但却被大卫凯恩寻获
But David Kane has found it.

788
01:22:58,850 --> 01:23:00,930
那力量也逐渐掌控他
And it's slowly possessing him.

789
01:23:01,930 --> 01:23:05,650
但即便冰帽融化 寇达斯仍无法重见天日
But even with the ice cap melting, Kordax still can't be freed.

790
01:23:05,650 --> 01:23:08,360
亚特兰用鲜血魔咒 将寇达斯封锁在笼牢中
Atlan used blood magic to seal Kordax in his prison.

791
01:23:08,360 --> 01:23:10,320
只有亚特兰才能释放他
Only Atlan himself could release him.

792
01:23:10,320 --> 01:23:14,820
黑蝠鲼不需要亚特兰本人 只需要他的血
Manta doesn't need Atlan himself. Manta needs Atlan's blood.

793
01:23:15,450 --> 01:23:17,280
血咒跟一般魔法不同 更像是DNA辨识
Blood magic isn't really magic, it's DNA.

794
01:23:17,280 --> 01:23:22,200
想开启寇达斯的笼牢 就需要以皇室血亲鲜血为钥
The key to Kordax's prison is the royal bloodline itself.

795
01:23:22,790 --> 01:23:26,170
意思是他需要你、我 或是亚瑟的血
That means he needs blood from either you, me or Arthur.

796
01:23:28,590 --> 01:23:29,750
我们是王室最后血脉
We're the end of the bloodline.

797
01:23:34,050 --> 01:23:35,220
不 我们不是
No, we're not.

798
01:23:36,640 --> 01:23:39,100
原本世界各地就频传野火灾情
...Wildfires would have made headlines across the world,

799
01:23:39,100 --> 01:23:41,390
现在更是几乎每周出现
but now, they're almost a weekly occurrence.

800
01:23:41,390 --> 01:23:44,640
此刻全球正见证前所未有的气候异象
We're witnessing unprecedented weather events across the globe,

801
01:23:44,640 --> 01:23:48,190
气象学家也不知该如何解释 全球气候的快速变迁
and meteorologists are at a loss to explain this rapid change in climate.

802
01:23:48,190 --> 01:23:50,020
从炽热的热浪和干旱
From sweltering heatwaves and droughts,

803
01:23:50,020 --> 01:23:53,530
不断打破高温记录 到暴雨和洪水
which are shattering temperature records, to torrential rains and floodings...

804
01:23:53,530 --> 01:23:55,280
-到底怎么回事? -飓风席卷东岸
- What is going on? - ...hurricane bearing down on the East Coast,

805
01:23:55,280 --> 01:23:58,370
让百万家庭面对断电...
leaving one million homes without power...

806
01:24:00,740 --> 01:24:03,040
现在再加上我们一家
Make that a million and one.

807
01:24:03,620 --> 01:24:05,710
我先去拿手电筒 小宝
I gotta get the flashlight, bubba.

808
01:24:22,430 --> 01:24:26,770
我先留你活口 好让他能亲眼看你送命
I'm gonna leave you alive, so he can watch you die.

809
01:24:35,400 --> 01:24:36,650
老爹
Dad!

810
01:24:36,650 --> 01:24:38,360
-汤姆 -老爹
- Tom! - Dad!

811
01:24:39,200 --> 01:24:40,660
汤姆
Tom!

812
01:24:41,740 --> 01:24:43,410
不 老爹
No! Dad!

813
01:24:43,410 --> 01:24:44,660
小亚瑟在哪?
Where's Junior?

814
01:24:46,870 --> 01:24:48,960
汤姆 不
Tom! No!

815
01:24:49,830 --> 01:24:50,880
抱歉 儿子
I'm sorry, son.

816
01:24:51,500 --> 01:24:52,630
小亚瑟在哪?
Where's Junior?

817
01:24:53,380 --> 01:24:56,220
黑蝠鲼...带走了小亚瑟
Manta... took Junior.

818
01:24:56,920 --> 01:24:58,760
-不 -不
- No! - No!

819
01:24:59,680 --> 01:25:01,220
不
No!

820
01:25:53,150 --> 01:25:54,820
（发射座标）

821
01:25:54,980 --> 01:25:56,150
（发射完毕）

822
01:25:57,070 --> 01:25:59,070
医务兵已将他的情况稳定下来
The medics have stabilized his condition.

823
01:25:59,070 --> 01:26:00,740
他不会有事
He will be okay.

824
01:26:00,740 --> 01:26:02,280
我们刚收到讯号
We just picked up a signal.

825
01:26:02,280 --> 01:26:06,830
很微弱 是从古老亚特兰提斯 声纳频率上传来的
It's faint, but it's broadcasting on an old Atlantean sonar frequency.

826
01:26:06,830 --> 01:26:08,660
并往南极洲移动
Headed to Antarctica.

827
01:26:09,910 --> 01:26:12,500
-去把小宝带回来 -我会的
- Bring our little one back. - I will.

828
01:26:14,080 --> 01:26:16,340
我曾梦想过此刻
I've dreamed of this.

829
01:26:16,340 --> 01:26:18,960
有朝一日你们俩能兄弟相挺
The two of you standing together as brothers.

830
01:26:22,890 --> 01:26:24,970
答应我你们会保护彼此
Promise me you will protect each other.

831
01:26:28,310 --> 01:26:30,140
答应我 欧姆
Promise me, Orm.

832
01:26:44,320 --> 01:26:45,700
去吧
Go.

833
01:27:11,430 --> 01:27:13,890
好炫的出行工具 涅罗斯
Great waves, Nereus.

834
01:27:13,890 --> 01:27:18,070
你的战舰很强大 但速度竟慢过海牛
Your warship is powerful, but it's slower than a sea cow.

835
01:27:18,730 --> 01:27:23,490
依我看还不如甩掉这破烂 轻骑出行
I say we ditch all this dead weight and travel light. Hmm?

836
01:27:23,490 --> 01:27:25,990
那敌方发射音波炮时要怎么办?
And what are you gonna do when he turns on that sonic cannon?

837
01:27:25,990 --> 01:27:30,580
我们唯一的胜算 就是用全方位压倒性的火力回击
Our only chance is to hit him with total overwhelming force from every direction.

838
01:27:30,580 --> 01:27:33,660
-不能让小亚瑟置身火线中 -我们还有什么选择?
- Not with Junior in the crossfire. - What choice do we have?

839
01:27:33,660 --> 01:27:35,750
我们无法抵抗那种炮火
We have no defense against that cannon.

840
01:27:35,750 --> 01:27:37,210
等等
Well, wait a minute.

841
01:27:37,210 --> 01:27:41,090
这种武器会发射音波 并干扰神经系统 对吧?
So this cannon sends out soundwaves that messes with our nervous system, right?

842
01:27:41,090 --> 01:27:44,050
没错 是超音波回波
That's right. Ultrasonic echoes.

843
01:27:44,050 --> 01:27:45,680
若我们发射同样频率的
Well, what if we disrupt those echoes

844
01:27:45,680 --> 01:27:47,550
另一种音波来干扰回波
with another soundwave on the same frequency,

845
01:27:47,550 --> 01:27:49,720
而且还更大声呢?
but just much, much louder?

846
01:27:49,720 --> 01:27:51,770
你想用魔法打败魔法?
You wanna disrupt their disruption?

847
01:27:52,430 --> 01:27:53,850
那会是容易的部分
Well, that's gonna be the easy part.

848
01:27:54,980 --> 01:27:56,980
拿上你们的武器
Take your weapons.

849
01:27:58,440 --> 01:28:00,190
准备好座骑
And ready your steeds.

850
01:28:20,630 --> 01:28:22,840
他是真的不喜欢你 对吧?
Really doesn't like you, does he?

851
01:28:53,950 --> 01:28:55,830
我们原本进展不错 博士
We made a lot of progress, doc.

852
01:28:55,830 --> 01:28:58,120
虽然他们在我们大功告成前毁了熔炉
They destroyed the furnace before we could finish the job,

853
01:28:58,120 --> 01:29:00,000
但我们很接近了
but we were damn close.

854
01:29:00,000 --> 01:29:02,630
只要再朝正确位置 射颗飞弹就能搞定一切
One well-placed missile should do the trick.

855
01:29:05,380 --> 01:29:07,050
我的老天 我们做了什么?
My God, what did we do?

856
01:29:07,800 --> 01:29:10,430
反正这世界原本已开了头
Nothing the world wasn't already doing.

857
01:29:10,430 --> 01:29:13,180
我们不过是让进程加快了几年
All we did was fast forward things a few years.

858
01:29:13,180 --> 01:29:16,680
冰帽还没完全融化 但我们扫描发现了一个弱点
The ice hasn't fully melted yet, but our scanning reveals a weak spot.

859
01:29:17,770 --> 01:29:18,600
这里
Here.

860
01:29:18,600 --> 01:29:21,230
从这里能让你直达寇达斯
This will lead you straight to Kordax.

861
01:29:23,110 --> 01:29:24,730
开启音波炮
Power up the sonic cannon.

862
01:29:26,360 --> 01:29:27,740
带上那小鬼 着装
Bag the child and suit up.

863
01:29:57,850 --> 01:29:59,940
队长 前方有多位敌军来袭
Captain, we have multiple incoming hostiles.

864
01:29:59,940 --> 01:30:01,730
（飞弹武装完成）

865
01:30:01,730 --> 01:30:03,020
你们来得太迟了
You're too late.

866
01:30:12,870 --> 01:30:13,820
等...
No.

867
01:30:39,770 --> 01:30:40,980
开始充电
Commence charge.

868
01:31:31,860 --> 01:31:34,240
你是开玩笑的吧
You've got to be kidding me.

869
01:32:11,280 --> 01:32:13,030
太神奇了
Astounding.

870
01:32:13,940 --> 01:32:18,660
（失落王国涅库斯）

871
01:32:55,570 --> 01:32:57,950
这里太大了 可能藏在任何地方
This place is immense. It could be anywhere.

872
01:32:57,950 --> 01:33:00,530
涅库斯的王座位于城市的中心
The throne of Necrus is in the heart of the city.

873
01:33:00,530 --> 01:33:02,910
-我感测到水中有东西 -所有人 点亮照明
- I sense something in the water. - Everyone, light it up.

874
01:33:08,080 --> 01:33:12,800
你不是说寇达斯把他的人民 都变成怪兽军团了吗?
Didn't you say that Kordax turned his people into an army of monsters?

875
01:33:12,800 --> 01:33:14,760
对 没错
Yes. I did.

876
01:33:14,760 --> 01:33:16,220
眼睛睁大了
Keep your eyes open.

877
01:33:16,840 --> 01:33:19,550
那很简单 反正我也闭不了眼
Well, that'll be easy. Mine don't close.

878
01:33:20,090 --> 01:33:22,300
大家保持备战 前方有东西逼近
Everyone stand ready. Something's coming.

879
01:33:27,230 --> 01:33:28,770
自由开火
Fire at will!

880
01:33:44,240 --> 01:33:45,700
我们得找方法离开此处
We need to find a way out of here.

881
01:33:46,330 --> 01:33:47,540
从这里应该能一路穿过去
I think this goes all the way through.

882
01:33:47,540 --> 01:33:50,040
我的军队能对付这些虾兵蟹将
My men and I can deal with these worms.

883
01:33:50,710 --> 01:33:52,920
你快去吧 把王子救回来
Go now and save the prince.

884
01:33:53,670 --> 01:33:55,050
谢谢你 殿下
Thank you, Your Highness.

885
01:33:57,420 --> 01:33:59,510
来啊 你们这些软脚虾
Come on, you spineless worms!

886
01:34:00,130 --> 01:34:01,430
放马过来
Bring it on!

887
01:35:10,370 --> 01:35:11,460
帮帮我
Help me!

888
01:36:14,600 --> 01:36:16,400
把孩子给我
Give me the child.

889
01:37:09,950 --> 01:37:14,080
你挑错日子良心发现了 博士
You picked the wrong day to grow a spine, doc.

890
01:37:17,750 --> 01:37:19,210
快赶到吊闸后方
Get behind the portcullis!

891
01:37:20,420 --> 01:37:22,210
我们需要关闭闸门
We need to close the gate!

892
01:38:00,170 --> 01:38:02,630
离我儿子远点
Get away from my son!

893
01:38:03,340 --> 01:38:06,670
反正用你的血也行
Your blood will do just fine.

894
01:38:08,130 --> 01:38:10,880
你想要血? 就自己来取
You want blood? Come get it!

895
01:38:25,190 --> 01:38:26,650
海王
Aquaman!

896
01:39:15,030 --> 01:39:18,790
你身穿我哥的盔甲 手拿他的三叉戟
You wear my brother's armor, and wield his trident,

897
01:39:18,790 --> 01:39:21,710
但你连他的一半都比不上
but you're only half the man he was.

898
01:39:23,040 --> 01:39:24,540
真可悲
How pathetic.

899
01:39:39,060 --> 01:39:40,180
梅拉
Mera!

900
01:39:55,820 --> 01:39:56,740
你先走
Go!

901
01:40:11,260 --> 01:40:12,340
梅拉
Mera...

902
01:40:14,340 --> 01:40:15,340
快逃
Run!

903
01:40:19,260 --> 01:40:21,560
将我从监禁中释放
Free me from my prison,

904
01:40:21,560 --> 01:40:26,900
我的所有力量就会为你所用
and all my power will be yours to wield as you desire.

905
01:41:02,970 --> 01:41:07,480
杀了他 你就能再度成为海洋领主
Kill him, and you will be Ocean Master again!

906
01:41:14,570 --> 01:41:17,860
不错 现在这样终于好一点了
Well, now this is certainly an improvement.

907
01:41:18,360 --> 01:41:20,660
强大的亚特兰提斯身躯
Powerful, Atlantean body.

908
01:41:20,660 --> 01:41:24,240
而且这个人比之前那个更恨你
And this one hates you more than the other one did.

909
01:41:24,240 --> 01:41:26,830
你说谎 别这样 小弟 我知道你听得见我
It's not true. Come on, little brother. I know you're in there.

910
01:41:26,830 --> 01:41:29,420
你看不出来吗? 你赢不了的
Don't you see? You can't win.

911
01:41:29,920 --> 01:41:32,800
你不是杀死你弟 就是等着自己受死
Either you kill your brother or you die.

912
01:41:48,020 --> 01:41:52,690
凭藉亚特兰的血脉 魔咒终被破解
By an Atlan's blood, this magic is broken.

913
01:42:06,000 --> 01:42:09,210
我的永夜已结束
My eternal night is ending.

914
01:42:16,630 --> 01:42:19,170
我受够跟你的傀儡对打了 寇达斯
I'm done fighting your puppets, Kordax.

915
01:42:20,380 --> 01:42:22,260
我要跟你对干
I'm coming for you.

916
01:42:25,390 --> 01:42:26,520
-给我 -不要
- Give it to me! - No!

917
01:42:26,520 --> 01:42:28,930
-我能了结这一切 -别让他夺走一切
- I can end this. - Don't let him take it!

918
01:42:28,930 --> 01:42:31,520
难道他抢走的还不够多吗?
Hasn't he taken enough already?

919
01:42:33,150 --> 01:42:34,440
放弃王位
Yield the throne.

920
01:42:34,440 --> 01:42:37,990
是时候让我重新承启天命了
It's time for me to reclaim my destiny.

921
01:42:37,990 --> 01:42:40,900
认为他能改变的想法实在太傻了
It would be foolish to think he could ever change.

922
01:42:40,900 --> 01:42:42,490
我知道你会做到
I knew you would do this.

923
01:42:42,910 --> 01:42:44,700
你才是独一无二的真正王者
You are the one true king.

924
01:42:44,700 --> 01:42:48,250
亚特兰提斯值得拥有真正的王者
Atlantis deserves its one true king.

925
01:42:50,580 --> 01:42:54,500
我才是独一无二的真正王者
I am the one true king!

926
01:43:02,130 --> 01:43:05,390
你知道 我曾经有一度非常想见你
You know, there was a time when I wanted to meet you more than anything.

927
01:43:06,180 --> 01:43:09,770
想让你知道你并不孤单 我俩能互相扶持
Let you know that you weren't alone, that we were in it together.

928
01:43:09,770 --> 01:43:11,980
答应我 你俩会保护彼此
Promise me you'll protect each other.

929
01:43:17,190 --> 01:43:20,860
来吧 小弟 让我们一起了结这个混蛋
Come on, little brother, let's end this bastard.

930
01:43:21,320 --> 01:43:23,740
我俩第一次见面时 我说的都是真心话
I meant what I said when I first met you.

931
01:43:24,200 --> 01:43:26,330
无论如何 你都不孤单
No matter what, you are not alone.

932
01:43:26,990 --> 01:43:28,290
我俩可以一起承担
We're in this together.

933
01:43:31,870 --> 01:43:33,210
你是我的兄弟
You are my brother.

934
01:43:38,800 --> 01:43:39,710
欧姆
Orm.

935
01:43:42,800 --> 01:43:44,300
放手吧
Let go.

936
01:43:58,610 --> 01:44:00,530
欧姆 放手吧
Orm, let it go.

937
01:44:19,550 --> 01:44:22,300
我终于重生了
I live again!

938
01:44:22,920 --> 01:44:28,510
为了此刻 我在黑暗中苦等数世纪
I have waited countless centuries in the dark for this moment.

939
01:44:34,730 --> 01:44:35,940
吃屎了
Shit.

940
01:44:43,610 --> 01:44:44,860
亚瑟
Arthur!

941
01:46:11,280 --> 01:46:12,700
绝不
Never.

942
01:46:20,870 --> 01:46:23,590
亚瑟 我们得走了 魔咒已经崩解
Arthur, we've gotta go. The magic is broken.

943
01:46:38,770 --> 01:46:39,890
我们快闪吧
Let's get outta here!

944
01:46:52,320 --> 01:46:53,490
快点
Hurry!

945
01:46:59,080 --> 01:47:00,000
没错
That's right!

946
01:47:00,000 --> 01:47:01,620
来吧 宝贝 好耶
Come on, baby! Yeah!

947
01:47:17,600 --> 01:47:18,430
好耶
Yeah!

948
01:47:38,990 --> 01:47:40,000
吾爱
My love.

949
01:47:42,870 --> 01:47:44,080
嗨 儿子
Hi, baby boy.

950
01:47:53,720 --> 01:47:54,590
老沈
Shin.

951
01:47:55,550 --> 01:47:56,550
谢谢你
Thank you.

952
01:48:03,100 --> 01:48:04,650
太神奇了
Astounding.

953
01:48:09,940 --> 01:48:12,650
看来大家都全身而退 很好 很好
All here looking intact. That's good. That's good.

954
01:48:13,070 --> 01:48:16,280
但我没有 我的螯足被砍断了
Well, I'm not. My claw got cut off.

955
01:48:16,280 --> 01:48:17,660
还是第二次
Again!

956
01:48:18,700 --> 01:48:21,080
你是最强悍的甲壳纲动物 殿下
You're one tough crustacean, Your Highness.

957
01:48:21,950 --> 01:48:24,330
依我来看 你的前罪已清
As far as I'm concerned, your debt is paid.

958
01:48:25,750 --> 01:48:27,580
但不是所有人都会同意这点
Not everybody's gonna see it that way though.

959
01:48:32,460 --> 01:48:34,930
真可惜你在战斗中不幸丧生了
It's too bad you went and had yourself killed back there.

960
01:48:36,970 --> 01:48:37,970
对
Yes.

961
01:48:37,970 --> 01:48:39,850
这么多浮冰
All this ice.

962
01:48:40,890 --> 01:48:43,020
要找到尸体可不容易
It'd be impossible to find the body.

963
01:48:44,770 --> 01:48:46,060
先低调一阵子
Just lay low for a while.

964
01:48:46,480 --> 01:48:47,980
但别跑太远
But don't go too far.

965
01:48:48,400 --> 01:48:50,400
我可能会需要你的辅佐
I may need to call you up for some advice.

966
01:48:50,400 --> 01:48:53,360
像是如何管理王国那类的事
You know, with the whole running the kingdom thing.

967
01:48:59,410 --> 01:49:00,530
谢谢你
Thank you...

968
01:49:02,370 --> 01:49:03,950
大哥
brother.

969
01:49:19,090 --> 01:49:21,180
你比你自己想像中做得好多了
You're not as bad at this as you think.

970
01:49:23,020 --> 01:49:25,770
亚特兰提斯的人民很幸运能够拥有你
The people of Atlantis are lucky to have you.

971
01:49:27,060 --> 01:49:28,850
你弥补了我所有的不足
You are everything I was not.

972
01:49:28,850 --> 01:49:31,940
就算前景再困难 你仍能坚持正道
You do the right thing when doing the wrong thing is much easier.

973
01:49:33,320 --> 01:49:37,860
你也愿意向往日宿敌开口求助
And you're willing to ask for help even from your worst enemy.

974
01:49:39,700 --> 01:49:42,580
虽然有时你感觉不知道自己在做什么
I know it may not feel like you know what you're doing sometimes, but...

975
01:49:42,580 --> 01:49:44,450
但请继续信任自己的直觉
keep trusting your instincts.

976
01:49:45,200 --> 01:49:48,670
若你起身领导 亚特兰提斯必将跟随
If you lead, Atlantis will follow.

977
01:49:51,460 --> 01:49:54,800
毕竟真正的王者会搭建桥梁
After all, a true king builds bridges, right?

978
01:49:56,090 --> 01:49:58,050
我以为那只是个隐喻
I thought that was just a metaphor.

979
01:50:00,430 --> 01:50:05,270
但你的隐喻刚刚拯救了全世界
Well, your metaphor might have just saved the world's ass.

980
01:50:29,420 --> 01:50:30,750
刚刚传来即时新闻
We've got breaking news.

981
01:50:30,750 --> 01:50:32,080
今日我们见证了历史
We are witnessing history.

982
01:50:32,080 --> 01:50:34,550
其所带来的后果是...
A moment the ramifications of which simply...

983
01:50:34,550 --> 01:50:35,590
无论如何强调都不为过
cannot be overstated.

984
01:50:38,590 --> 01:50:39,680
海底王国
A first contact...

985
01:50:39,680 --> 01:50:41,260
亚特兰提斯首度主动现身
...with the undersea nation of Atlantis.

986
01:50:41,260 --> 01:50:45,510
一个隐身数千年的文明即将解密
An entire civilization hidden for thousands of years about to be revealed.

987
01:50:51,980 --> 01:50:54,730
可以说世界从此将大为不同
I think it's safe to say the world will never be the same.

988
01:50:54,730 --> 01:50:57,110
亚特兰提斯之王联系了联合国
The King of Atlantis has reached out to the United Nations

989
01:50:57,110 --> 01:50:59,190
正式请求成为会员国
and will be officially seeking membership.

990
01:50:59,190 --> 01:51:02,410
并有望提出共同努力方案 来扭转气候问题
And is expected to propose a joint effort to reverse the climate issues.

991
01:51:02,410 --> 01:51:05,660
据说这是与联合国在历经数周
We are told that this was the result of weeks of secret negotiations

992
01:51:05,660 --> 01:51:08,620
-密谈后的结果 -本台将与艾力斯岛连线
- with the United Nations. - We now go live to Ellis Island,

993
01:51:08,620 --> 01:51:10,620
直播亚特兰提斯的首位官方大使
where the first official ambassador from Atlantis

994
01:51:10,620 --> 01:51:12,670
在联合国所发表的谈话
is about to address the United Nations.

995
01:51:21,840 --> 01:51:24,760
今天我身为两个世界的代表来此
I come here today as a representative of two worlds.

996
01:51:25,390 --> 01:51:27,810
陆地与海洋
The land and the sea.

997
01:51:31,390 --> 01:51:35,690
我来到这里证明了两地都将迎来改变
And I stand here as proof that change is coming to both.

998
01:51:36,150 --> 01:51:40,280
为应对全球危机我呼吁全球合作
And I'm calling for global unity for a global crisis.

999
01:51:41,530 --> 01:51:45,490
好推进两地之间的和谐 以及我们世界的自然平衡
To finally bring harmony between us and the natural balance of our world.

1000
01:51:46,660 --> 01:51:50,910
亚特兰提斯随时准备提供协助 贡献我方的科学与技术
Atlantis stands ready to help contribute its science and technology.

1001
01:51:50,910 --> 01:51:54,420
凭藉你们对大气的了解 以及我们对海洋的了解
And with your knowledge of the air, and our knowledge of the seas,

1002
01:51:55,080 --> 01:51:57,040
我们可以一起写下彼此故事的下一章
together we can write the next chapter in our story,

1003
01:51:57,800 --> 01:51:59,210
而不是结局
rather than its ending.

1004
01:52:00,210 --> 01:52:03,260
有时我们的分歧会看似太过极端
Sometimes it's gonna seem like our differences are too extreme,

1005
01:52:03,760 --> 01:52:05,930
但我们只需要扪心自问
but all we have to do is look beneath the surface,

1006
01:52:07,260 --> 01:52:11,180
并了解到我们同在此星球上 更有着相同的目标和远景
to see that we're all here on this planet with the same goals and aspirations.

1007
01:52:11,560 --> 01:52:12,980
-即便两方的风俗 -给你
- Even when our customs... - Here you go.

1008
01:52:12,980 --> 01:52:15,560
-是如此迥异与陌生 -啤酒与起司汉堡
- ...might seem strange and unfamiliar. - Beer and a cheeseburger.

1009
01:52:15,560 --> 01:52:17,650
像你要求的那样额外多汁
Extra greasy like you asked for.

1010
01:52:19,480 --> 01:52:21,900
但透过克服我们的偏见
And by overcoming our prejudices,

1011
01:52:21,900 --> 01:52:24,490
我们会变得更加强大 并更为了解我们自己
we'll become stronger and learn more about ourselves.

1012
01:52:25,610 --> 01:52:28,990
我们可以抓住此契机 为了我们的孩子与家庭
We can seize this moment to create a better more hopeful future,

1013
01:52:29,370 --> 01:52:32,450
创造更美好并更有希望的未来
for our children, and our families.

1014
01:52:34,290 --> 01:52:35,960
我的名字是亚瑟库瑞
My name is Arthur Curry.

1015
01:52:36,250 --> 01:52:39,750
我是海底王国亚特兰提斯的法定君主
I'm the rightful sovereign of the undersea nation of Atlantis.

1016
01:52:39,750 --> 01:52:41,800
我是一位父亲、兄长
I'm a father, a brother,

1017
01:52:41,800 --> 01:52:44,470
战士 与友人
a warrior and a friend.

1018
01:52:45,630 --> 01:52:47,640
我是亚特兰提斯之王
I'm the King of Atlantis.

1019
01:52:49,100 --> 01:52:50,640
我是海王
I am Aquaman.

1020
02:03:32,160 --> 02:03:35,990
海王 失落王国

